  ('dietitian-moex-01597', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-109-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據食品良好衛生規範準則，餐飲業者若以乾熱殺菌法對餐具進行殺菌處理，其條件為何？', '["攝氏80度以上，加熱90分鐘以上", "攝氏90度以上，加熱60分鐘以上", "攝氏100度以上，加熱40分鐘以上", "攝氏110度以上，加熱30分鐘以上"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c654f2148d1f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "81cb56c5da63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01598', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-109-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據食品良好衛生規範準則，冷藏真空包裝即食食品保存期限可大於10日，其應具備之保存條 件何者錯誤？', '["添加亞硝酸鹽或硝酸鹽", "水活性在0.94以上", "pH＜4.6", "具有可抑制肉毒桿菌生長之條件"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c654f2148d1f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "81cb56c5da63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "103", "s": "0206", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
